      "description": "Employee and manager self-service portal coordinating cross-domain lifecycle: onboarding intake from ATS, lifecycle change requests, leave/absence visibility, and offboarding handoffs to ITSM/IGA/PAYROLL. Workflow surface on top of HCM-CORE-WORKER and HCM-ORG-POSITIONS, no masters of its own."
    },
    {
      "code": "HCM-ORG-POSITIONS",
      "name": "Organization and Position Management",
