      "description": "Maintain the authoritative worker record (profiles, addresses, national IDs, emergency contacts, dependents, work-eligibility documents) and employment contracts; design the org structure with job profiles, positions, and org units; plan headcount against budgeted roles; and drive every people change through governed lifecycle workflows: hiring and onboarding, transfers, promotions, leaves, and offboarding. Let employees and managers raise and track self-service change requests while HR keeps approval control, and keep compliance evidence current.",
